<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ض ل ع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٣٧ - ض ل ع]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضلِعَ يَضلَع، ضَلَعًا، فهو ضَلِع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضلِع الغُصنُ:</span> ضلَع؛ اعوجَّ وانثنى <span class="c1">"ضلِع العودُ/ السيفُ- ضلِعت العصا"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ضلِع الظَّمآنُ:</span> شبع وارتوى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>